<Page x:Class="CryptoApp.AboutPage"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
      xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" 
      xmlns:local="clr-namespace:CryptoApp"
      mc:Ignorable="d" 
      d:DesignHeight="700" d:DesignWidth="1500"
      Title="AboutPage">

    <Grid>
        <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
            <ColumnDefinition Width="3*"/>
            <ColumnDefinition Width="1*"/>
        </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>

        <StackPanel Grid.Column="0" Margin="126 69 0 0">
            <TextBlock Text="About" Width="200" Height="50" Margin="0 10 9 15" FontSize="48" FontFamily="Inter">
                <TextBlock.Effect>
                    <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="4" Direction="-90" RenderingBias="Performance" Opacity="0.2" ShadowDepth="2"/>
                </TextBlock.Effect>
            </TextBlock>
            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Text="Welcome to our Cryptocurrency Converter App!

At Cryptocurrency Converter, we aim to provide you with a seamless and efficient way to explore and convert various cryptocurrencies. Whether you're a seasoned trader, a crypto enthusiast, or simply curious about the world of digital currencies, our app is designed to meet your needs.

With our app, you can stay up-to-date with the latest cryptocurrency prices, track market trends, and easily convert one cryptocurrency to another. We support a wide range of cryptocurrencies, including Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin, Ripple, and many more. Our app retrieves real-time data from reliable sources, ensuring accurate and reliable conversion rates.

Key Features:

Real-time cryptocurrency prices: Stay informed about the current market prices of your favorite cryptocurrencies.
Easy conversion: Seamlessly convert one cryptocurrency to another with just a few clicks.
Comprehensive currency support: Access a vast selection of cryptocurrencies and explore their conversion rates.
Historical data: Analyze the historical performance of cryptocurrencies to make informed investment decisions.
User-friendly interface: Enjoy a clean and intuitive user interface that makes navigating and using our app a breeze.
Whether you're looking to compare different cryptocurrencies, calculate the value of your holdings, or simply explore the exciting world of digital assets, Cryptocurrency Converter is your go-to app. We're committed to providing you with a reliable, secure, and user-friendly experience.

Start your crypto journey today with Cryptocurrency Converter! Stay informed, make informed decisions, and explore the endless possibilities of the digital currency market." Width="900" Height="900" Margin="0 0 9 0" FontSize="24" FontFamily="Inter">
                <TextBlock.Effect>
                    <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="4" Direction="-90" RenderingBias="Performance" Opacity="0.2" ShadowDepth="2"/>
                </TextBlock.Effect>
            </TextBlock>
        </StackPanel>

    </Grid>
</Page>
